      <profileDesc>
         <abstract>
            <p>One of the two homilies on Melchizedek's origin attributed to <persName
                  ref="PRS3255CyrilI"/>. Both homilies according to <bibl><ptr
                     target="bm:Dillmann1866Chrestomathia"/></bibl> were translated from the Greek,
               but the original is lost and the Ethiopic version is the only known one, see
                     <bibl><ptr target="bm:CPG3"/></bibl>. Its Gǝʿǝz versions is known to be transmitted as
               part of <title ref="LIT3309Qerellos"/> or along the <title ref="LIT2365Storyo"/> .
            </p>
         </abstract>
